<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='452000' id='t-452000'>by 87 percent --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='454000' id='t-454000'>a function of both increase in sales</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='456000' id='t-456000'>and lowering of costs.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='458000' id='t-458000'>You know, the average grocery store today</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='460000' id='t-460000'>offers you 45,000 products.</span>
