</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 8:11
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='480000' id='t-480000'>Now in the financial savings world,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='482000' id='t-482000'>I think one of the best examples that has recently come out</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='485000' id='t-485000'>on how to best manage the choice offerings</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='488000' id='t-488000'>has actually been something that David Laibson was heavily involved in designing,</span>
