<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='497000' id='t-497000'>in a lifecycle fund.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='499000' id='t-499000'>For those people who actually want to choose,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='501000' id='t-501000'>they're given 20 funds,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='503000' id='t-503000'>not 300 or more funds.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='505000' id='t-505000'>You know, often, people say,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='507000' id='t-507000'>&quot;I don't know how to cut.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='509000' id='t-509000'>They're all important choices.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='511000' id='t-511000'>And the first thing I do is I ask the employees,</span>
