</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 8:52
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='521000' id='t-521000'>Now before we started our session this afternoon,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='524000' id='t-524000'>I had a chat with Gary.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='526000' id='t-526000'>And Gary said that he would be willing</span>
