<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='531000' id='t-531000'>an all-expenses-paid free vacation</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='534000' id='t-534000'>to the most beautiful road in the world.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='538000' id='t-538000'>Here's a description of the road.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='541000' id='t-541000'>And I'd like you to read it.</span>
