<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='556000' id='t-556000'>All right, let me show you some more about this.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='559000' id='t-559000'>(Laughter)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='562000' id='t-562000'>You guys knew there was a trick, didn't you.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='569000' id='t-569000'>(Honk)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='571000' id='t-571000'>Now who's ready to go on this trip.</span>
