<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='581000' id='t-581000'>All right.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='583000' id='t-583000'>Now in fact,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='585000' id='t-585000'>you had objectively more information</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='587000' id='t-587000'>the first time around than the second time around,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='589000' id='t-589000'>but I would venture to guess</span>
