<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='685000' id='t-685000'>The third technique: Categorization.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='688000' id='t-688000'>We can handle more categories</span>
