<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='693000' id='t-693000'>So for example,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='695000' id='t-695000'>here's a study we did in a magazine aisle.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='697000' id='t-697000'>It turns out that in Wegmans grocery stores</span>
