<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='708000' id='t-708000'>But you know what?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='710000' id='t-710000'>If I show you 600 magazines</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='712000' id='t-712000'>and I divide them up into 10 categories,</span>
