</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
12:24
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='733000' id='t-733000'>Here are two different jewelry displays.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='736000' id='t-736000'>One is called &quot;Jazz&quot; and the other one is called &quot;Swing.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='739000' id='t-739000'>If you think the display on the left is Swing</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='742000' id='t-742000'>and the display on the right is Jazz,</span>
