<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='749000' id='t-749000'>Okay, there's some.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='751000' id='t-751000'>If you think the one on the left is Jazz and the one on the right is Swing,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='753000' id='t-753000'>clap your hands.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='755000' id='t-755000'>Okay, a bit more.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='757000' id='t-757000'>Now it turns out you're right.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='759000' id='t-759000'>The one on the left is Jazz and the one on the right is Swing,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='761000' id='t-761000'>but you know what?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='763000' id='t-763000'>This is a highly useless categorization scheme.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='766000' id='t-766000'>(Laughter)</span>
